---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Ellofant - Leading the Business Revolution">
  <main>
    <section class="about-hero">
      <h1>About AI Innovate</h1>
      <p>Pioneering the future of artificial intelligence to solve complex challenges and drive innovation.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="our-story">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>Founded in 2020, AI Innovate emerged from a vision to democratize artificial intelligence and make it accessible to businesses of all sizes. Our team of world-class researchers and engineers is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of what's possible with AI.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mission-vision">
      <div class="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To empower organizations with cutting-edge AI solutions that drive growth, efficiency, and innovation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="vision">
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>A world where AI enhances human potential, solves global challenges, and creates a more sustainable future for all.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team">
      <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>Dr. Emily Chen</h3>
          <p class="role">Chief AI Scientist</p>
          <p>With a Ph.D. in Machine Learning from MIT, Dr. Chen leads our research initiatives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>Michael Johnson</h3>
          <p class="role">CEO</p>
          <p>A veteran tech entrepreneur with 20 years of experience in scaling startups.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <h3>Sarah Williams</h3>
          <p class="role">Head of Engineering</p>
          <p>Former Google engineer specializing in large-scale AI systems deployment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values">
      <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Innovation: Constantly pushing the boundaries of AI technology</li>
        <li>Integrity: Upholding the highest ethical standards in AI development</li>
        <li>Collaboration: Fostering partnerships to create impactful solutions</li>
        <li>Excellence: Delivering exceptional results for our clients</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
      <h2>Join Us in Shaping the Future</h2>
      <p>Explore career opportunities at AI Innovate and be part of the AI revolution.</p>
      <a href="/careers" class="button">View Open Positions</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

